OL,3,CSeven British people died in wildfire
OL,4,Cin southern Spain, police confirm
OL,6,FSeven British people were among those
OL,7,Fwho died in a wildfire in southern
OL,8,FSpain, local authorities confirmed on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FThe Los Gallardos blaze engulfed 70
OL,12,Fsquare kilometers (27 square miles) of
OL,13,Fforest and farmland on July 9.
OL,15,FA 93-year-old English woman, who died
OL,16,Fin hospital from sustained injuries,
OL,17,Fwas the latest victim to be
OL,18,Fidentified, bringing the death toll to
OL,19,F13.
