OL,3,CSeven British people died in wildfire
OL,4,Cin southern Spain, police confirm
OL,6,FSpanish police said the other victims
OL,7,Fwho have been identified include three
OL,8,Fpeople from Belgium, one from France,
OL,9,Fand one from the United States, as
OL,10,Fwell as one Spanish citizen.
OL,12,FFamilies of all 13 victims have been
OL,13,Finformed, the police said.
OL,15,FBritish couple Pete and Fran Gillam
OL,16,Fwere among those killed in the fire,
OL,17,Fwhich broke out in Bedar, a town in
OL,18,FSpain's Almeria province with a
OL,19,Fpopulation of less than 1,000.
