OL,3,CSeven British people died in wildfire
OL,4,Cin southern Spain, police confirm
OL,6,FPosting on social media their
OL,7,Fdaughter, Danielle Gillam-Kirton, from
OL,8,FSheffield said they are "heartbroken"
OL,9,Fand "trying to come to terms with the
OL,10,Fdevastating news".
OL,12,FFour bodies were found in a burnt-out
OL,13,Fcar with a ride-sided steering wheel,
OL,14,Fimplying they were British.
OL,16,FHelicopters dropped water as hundreds
OL,17,Fof firefighters worked to tackle the
OL,18,Finferno.
OL,20,FSpain has seen many wildfires this
OL,21,Fmonth.
